      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t a showpiece, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants simple transportation, a project, or a handy spare vehicle. It has the usual wear you\u2019d expect at this stage, but it still offers real value and a chance to get behind the wheel without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re practical and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, this could be a great fit.",
